com.facebook.buck.android.resources

Class ResourceTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.resources.ResChunk
      • com.facebook.buck.android.resources.ResourceTable

  • public class ResourceTable
extends ResChunk
    A ResourceTable is the top-level representation of resources.arsc. It consists of a header: ResTable_header u32 chunk_type u32 header_size u32 chunk_size u32 package_count

    The header is followed by a StringPool and then package_count packages.

    In practice, aapt always generates .arsc files with package_count == 1.
